document_data.mainbody:
oguerun Alley was a small back alley that was located in the city of Waterdeep.
Roguerun Alley was located in the northwest section of Waterdeeps Sea Ward. The alley was situated in a small neighborhood located in between the Street of Glances and Breezes Cut, branching from Breezes Cut in the north, passing through the neighborhood, and exiting to join Westwall Street.
